{"word":"σοβέω","slug":"σοβέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n95567\" key=\"sobe/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σοβ-έω</orth>, <sense id=\"n95567.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">scare away</tr_> birds, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἡμεῖς δὲ . ., οὐ σοβοῦντος οὐδενὸς ἀνεπτόμεσθ᾽</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg006.perseus-grc1:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Av.\">Av.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">34</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπειδὴ τουτονὶ σεσοβήκαμεν</foreign> (just above he had been called <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στροῦθος</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:211\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">211</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ς. τὰς ἀλεκτρυόνας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0497.tlg001:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Pl.Com.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐ σοβήσετ᾽ ἔξω τὰς ὄρνιθας ἀφ᾽ ἡμῶν</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0541.tlg001:167\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Men.\">Men.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">167</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τέττιγας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:556b:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">556b14</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μυίας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg009:25:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Char.\">Char.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25.5</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drive along</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὥσπερ αἰπόλιον . . αὐτοὺς τῇ ῥάβδῳ ς</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg016:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cat.\">Cat.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔχοντες ξύλα σοβοῦσι τὴν ὕλην</foreign> they <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">scare</tr_> the wood (i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">beat</tr_> it so as to put up the birds), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:620a:35\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">620a35</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n95567.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drive away, clear away</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὴν κόνιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg013.perseus-grc1:5:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href